OL,3,CInvestigation launched into council
OL,4,Cworker's 'racist rant' on social media
OL,6,FAn investigation has been launched
OL,7,Finto a "racist" video of a council
OL,8,Fworker who said a "secret army" of
OL,9,Frefugees was coming to the UK and
OL,10,Fpreparing for a civil war.
OL,12,FThe worker made the comments on a
OL,13,FYoutube video that was published on 4
OL,14,FDecember 2025, in which he can be seen
OL,15,Fwearing his Sefton Council high-vis
OL,16,Funiform and drinking a can of lager.
