OL,3,CInvestigation launched into council
OL,4,Cworker's 'racist rant' on social media
OL,6,FThe video, which has been viewed more
OL,7,Fthan a million times across Instagram,
OL,8,FTikTok, and Youtube, was reported to
OL,9,FSefton Council which has now launched
OL,10,Fan investigation into the worker.
OL,12,FThe council has confirmed the man was
OL,13,Fone of its staff members and labelled
OL,14,Fhis comments "racist" and "divisive".
OL,16,FThe video was uploaded by a popular
OL,17,FYoutuber EmanRTN, who has more than a
OL,18,Fmillion followers and typically
OL,19,Fquizzes members of the public.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
