OL,3,CInvestigation launched into council
OL,4,Cworker's 'racist rant' on social media
OL,6,FIn the video, which was filmed on Lord
OL,7,FStreet in Liverpool, the staff member
OL,8,Fsays: "I feel like getting on a boat,
OL,9,Fgetting to Dover, come over, paint
OL,10,Fmyself f***ing black and get
OL,11,Feverything for free. It's disgusting,
OL,12,FI'm ready for a civil war."
OL,14,FExpressing his views on asylum
OL,15,Fseekers, he continued: "This is a
OL,16,Fsecret army coming in. This is nothing
OL,17,Fto do with them being in war torn
OL,18,Fcountries and all that crap. That's a
OL,19,Fload of bullsh*t."
