OL,6,FHe added: "They're coming here to kill
OL,7,Fus, to take over our country, and our
OL,8,Fgovernment are allowing it. It's sick."
OL,10,FHe concluded: "They're coming here to
OL,11,Fdestroy our country, not fight for our
OL,12,Fcountry, destroy our country, and when
OL,13,FI see them now, I'm ready for a civil
OL,14,Fwar."
OL,16,FThe man is seen to become increasingly
OL,17,Fanimated before apologising for his
OL,18,Ftone, eventually holding up a can of
OL,19,Flager and admitting "I've had a bevy".
