OL,3,CInvestigation launched into council
OL,4,Cworker's 'racist rant' on social media
OL,6,FReferring to the footage, a
OL,7,Fspokesperson for the local authority
OL,8,Fsaid: "We're aware of the video and
OL,9,Fthe matter is being dealt with
OL,10,Finternally.
OL,12,F"The comments are racist and in no way
OL,13,Freflect the views of Sefton Council.
OL,15,F"Our borough is one that is diverse
OL,16,Fand inclusive and the focus should be
OL,17,Fon all the good work taking place in
OL,18,Four communities to foster good
OL,19,Frelations, and not the views of an
OL,20,Findividual that only serves to cause
OL,21,Fdivision."
